These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: juice, iced-tea, sprite, tea
Pet: turtle, goldfish, ferret, pony
1. Pet:pony is on the left of Beverage:sprite##1
2. Beverage:juice is on the left of Pet:goldfish##1
3. Beverage:tea is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:ferret is on the left or right of Pet:pony##3
5. Beverage:juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | juice | iced-tea | tea | sprite |
| Pet        | turtle | goldfish   | pony | ferret    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: romance, drama, sports, animation
Nationality: british, thai, turkish, argentine
1. Movie-Genre:drama is on the left of Movie-Genre:animation##1
2. Nationality:british is on the left of Nationality:turkish##1
3. Nationality:turkish is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:british == Movie-Genre:romance##1
5. Nationality:thai is on the right of Nationality:turkish##1
6. Nationality:british == Movie-Genre:romance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | romance  | drama  | animation |
| Nationality   | argentine    | british | turkish | thai    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: papaya, orange, onion, tomato
Movie-Genre: drama, sports, zombie, horror
1. Food:tomato is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:horror##3
2. Food:onion is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:horror is on the left or right of Food:orange##3
4. Movie-Genre:horror is on the right of Movie-Genre:zombie##1
5. Movie-Genre:drama is in an odd position##4
6. Food:orange is on the right of Food:onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | tomato | onion | orange    | papaya      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie        | horror     | drama | sports |

