.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: chess, magic-tricks, fishing, baking
Music-Genre: metal, trance, salsa, jazz
1. Hobby:magic-tricks is between Music-Genre:metal and Music-Genre:jazz##2
2. Hobby:baking is on the left of Hobby:chess##1
3. Music-Genre:salsa is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:trance is on the left of Music-Genre:jazz##1
5. Music-Genre:trance is on the right of Hobby:chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | baking | chess | magic-tricks | fishing |
| Music-Genre   | salsa       | metal   | trance    | jazz  |

