.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: trance, funk, pop, techno
Nationality: brazilian, turkish, colombian, japanese
1. Music-Genre:pop is on the right of Nationality:japanese##1
2. Nationality:turkish == Music-Genre:techno##1
3. Nationality:colombian is on the right of Music-Genre:trance##1
4. Music-Genre:funk is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:pop is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:brazilian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | trance    | pop   | techno       |
| Nationality   | brazilian | japanese | colombian | turkish |

