.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: fanta, iced-tea, sprite, water
Music-Genre: folk, hip-hop, country, soul
1. Beverage:fanta == Music-Genre:soul##1
2. Music-Genre:folk is on the right of Beverage:fanta##1
3. Music-Genre:soul is between Music-Genre:folk and Beverage:sprite##2
4. Beverage:fanta is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:soul is on the left or right of Music-Genre:folk##3
6. Beverage:iced-tea is on the left or right of Music-Genre:hip-hop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | sprite   | fanta | water |
| Music-Genre   | country | hip-hop | soul        | folk    |

