.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: lemonade, cola, sprite, coffee
Food: pear, plum, cranberry, pineapple
1. Food:plum is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:sprite is on the left or right of Beverage:lemonade##3
3. Beverage:coffee is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:cranberry is on the left of Food:pineapple##1
5. Food:pineapple is on the right of Beverage:lemonade##1
6. Food:cranberry is in an even position##4
7. Food:pear == Beverage:cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | coffee | lemonade    | sprite       | cola |
| Food       | plum  | cranberry | pineapple | pear  |

